item.title: FEIW Female Entrepreneurship Last Call
item.description: Margaret Durand was in touch about the enterprise development programme for women in business that she is involved with. They have a LAST CALL for applicants for their intensive tailored 6 month programme to aid women in business in the South East achieve their growth goals. There are very few places left so if anyone is interested they should contact Margaret ASAP on mdurand AT wit DOT ie or visit the website www.
